reviews.review_text: I Remember this 4 stars Not perfect but it sure was a good time in so many ways. Miss those days and moments. Didn't get in 12/31 but they rolled out a speaker into the lot so we could hear the show. Those were the good old days...................................

Oakland 12/30/86 This is very nice for an 80's show as iI find 69'-74' ny favorite period.Jerry is back with a vengeance and the band is well played.Set 1 has some pretty decent moments but set2 has the honey.Just some really gr8 stuff .Ofcourse its worth a listen.Thanks as always Mr.Charlie Miller gr8 work all around.
